{"tid":1880322,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人就係犯賤嘅","createTime":"2020-02-14T18:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-29T14:54:43.000Z","uid":312733,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"27dd6d5064707275706f049c65749b719d451f14","tid":1880322,"uid":312733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T18:22:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">明明大家都攤開晒講大家都鐘意對方<br />\n但係你依然好似唔嗲唔吊咁，冇任何行動<br />\n究竟我係咩<br />\n我唔主動搵你 你就真係可以唔揾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係你心目中係咩地位？<br />\n點解係都要我做主動嗰個<br />\n又或者我係係到期待緊啲咩，期待你會問吓我今日做咗啲咩？期待你會主動表達自己嘅感情？定係期待你可以秒回到我？<br />\n算啦 有時真係好攰，但係又唔想咁樣完<br />\n總之 我好犯賤</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n叫完春又會繼續搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414335bbeadd9bcaa2edb5d4100927bfcbcc602b","tid":1880322,"uid":208285,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T18:26:23.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"e8b568c387638f68aad2dcb4a69c4cb8f87a682c","tid":1880322,"uid":293667,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T18:28:14.000Z","msg":"真心中意你自然會主動搵你<br />\n唔主動=你可有 可冇"},{"pid":"d207fcbff9b985a8aec8361d8e2f380fda3b196c","tid":1880322,"uid":14975,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T18:28:20.000Z","msg":"起碼你仲可以搵到佢<br />\n我已經搵唔到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a5cdff56c27c46f30b1e026d9a3519cbd7f314","tid":1880322,"uid":312733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e8b568c387638f68aad2dcb4a69c4cb8f87a682c","tid":1880322,"uid":293667,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T18:28:14.000Z","msg":"真心中意你自然會主動搵你<br />\n唔主動=你可有 可冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T18:31:57.000Z","msg":"唉，我明呀<br />\n但係我又唔捨得佢⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好驚佢唔要我 可能係我睇得佢太重要"},{"pid":"530eb8a9595c8796968f20f39d79695d3ecd1fb6",